(47, 53, 'Thematic Health Nutrition Population (HNP) Data', '', 'Thematic HNP data covers indicators on  themes such as population dynamics, nutrition, reproductive health, health financing, health workforce and health facilities use, immunization, malaria and tuberculosis, HIV/AIDS, by country and income/regional groups for 1990, 2000, 2010 and the most recent year available.', 'http://datatopics.worldbank.org/hnp/ThematicData', 'Time series', 'English', 'Annual', 'WLD, EAP, ECA, LAC, MNA, SAS, SSA, HIC, LMY, IBRD, IDA', 'National', 0, 'Health, Social Development', 'Annually', 'April', '06 Jul 2016', 'data@worldbank.org', '', 'Query tool', '', 'HealthStats, World Bank Group', 'http://data.worldbank.org/data catalog/thematic HNP data', 4, '1990   2014', '0', '', '');
