(106, 117, 'Listening to LAC', 'L2L', 'Household survey data in Peru and Honduras, collected over a six month period spanning 2010 2011 for a pilot exercise to determine feasibility of mobile data collection. Some of the data (baseline) was collected face to face and other data was collected using mobile phones monthly in Peru and weekly or bi weekly in Honduras.', '', 'Survey(Microdata)', 'English', '', 'LAC', 'National', 2, 'Poverty', 'No further updates planned', '', '04 Jun 2015', 'Amparo Ballivian (aballivian@worldbank.org)', '', '', '', '', 'http://data.worldbank.org/data catalog/listening to lac', 0, '', '', '', ''),
(107, 118, 'India Power Sector Review', '', 'This database underpins the analysis in the report    More Power to India: The Challenge of Electricity Distribution   . The database is a collection of primary and secondary data on the Indian power sector, collected at the utility and state levels. It covers 87 power utilities and 29 states and spreads over the years 2003 to 2011 across dimensions such as operational and financial performance, market structure, implementation of reforms and corporate and regulatory governance.', 'http://databank.worldbank.org/data/views/variableselection/selectvariables.aspx source india_power sector review database', 'Time series', '', 'Annual', 'SAS', 'Business or firm, National, Sub national', 1, 'Energy & Mining', 'No fixed schedule', '', '20 Jun 2014', 'data@worldbank.org', '', 'Bulk download, Query tool', 'India Power Sector Review (Excel)   ZIP(640 KB) http://databank.worldbank.org/data/download/India_PSR_excel.zip;India Power Sector Review (CSV)   ZIP(85 KB) http://databank.worldbank.org/data/download/India_PSR_csv.zip', '', 'http://data.worldbank.org/data catalog/india power sector review', 0, '2003   2011', '', '', ''),
(108, 119, 'Country Partnership Strategy for India (FY2013   17)', 'IndiaCPS', 'Indian sub national (state) indicators on various economic and social sectors relevant to the country partnership strategy', 'http://databank.worldbank.org/data/views/variableselection/selectvariables.aspx source country partnership strategy for india (fy2013 17)', 'Time series', 'English', 'Annual', 'SAS', 'Sub national', 1, 'Agriculture & Rural Development, Economy & Growth, Education, Energy & Mining, Financial Sector, Health, Infrastructure, Labor & Social Protection, Poverty, Social Development, Urban Development', 'No fixed schedule', '', '22 May 2015', 'data@worldbank.org', 'The data in this dataset do not imply any judgment on the part of The World Bank Group concerning the legal status of the states and union territories of India, nor do they imply endorsement or acceptance of territorial boundaries. Data at the State and Union Territory levels in India are from publicly accessible web sites of the Ministries or Departments of the Government of India. Data on the financial inclusion index are from CRISIL   an analytics and ratings firm. The World Bank does not gua', 'API, Bulk download, Query tool', 'India CPS (Excel)   ZIP (210 KB) http://databank.worldbank.org/data/download/India_CPS_excel.zip;India CPS (CSV)   ZIP (69 KB) http://databank.worldbank.org/data/download/India_CPS_csv.zip', '', 'http://data.worldbank.org/data catalog/india cps', 18, '1951   2011', '1', 'http://data.worldbank.org/developers', '41'),
